874
00:49:27,465 --> 00:49:29,717
I'm sure you're all aware
that ahead of this launch,

875
00:49:29,800 --> 00:49:31,886
we've secured convertible bonds
from Kaiserman Capital

876
00:49:31,969 --> 00:49:33,512
