- Just a scoundrel I know.

1004
00:56:32,514 --> 00:56:34,099
Let us put the past behind us

1005
00:56:34,182 --> 00:56:36,810
and start anew like respectable gentlemen.

1006
00:56:36,894 --> 00:56:38,103
Huzzah!

1007
